  "text": "To determine fixational stability and proximity to the anatomical fovea, the location of the retina used for fixation (preferred retinal locus) was determined by recording a video while the patient looked at a target that was provided through modulation of the AOSLO scanning raster. [CITATION_1] As such, the fixation target was encoded directly into the video, and the region of the retina used to fixate the target was determined using custom image analysis tools written in MATLAB.",
